snippet.title: Wicked Tuna 4P: Dive into the Thrilling World of Deep-Sea Fishing!
snippet.description:
Experience the excitement of deep-sea fishing with UNIS' arcade-style adaptation, Wicked Tuna! Based on the popular "Wicked Tuna" reality TV show, this unique game puts you in the captain's seat as you aim to catch the best quality bluefin tuna and become the top fisherman. Featuring original voiceovers recorded by the show's cast, Wicked Tuna is a coin-op amusement game unlike any other. Select your favorite captains and boats, embark on fishing expeditions, and compete in both single player and multiplayer modes. The game uses rotating controllers with force-feedback and adjustable reel tension to provide a realistic fishing experience. With stunning graphics on a whopping 85" monitor, Wicked Tuna is sure to stand out in any location. Immerse yourself in the thrill of deep-sea fishing like never before! 



For sales inquiries: sales@unistechnology.com
